  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><span class="geolocation-title"><strong>Our Chalet, Xtra Chalet &amp; Chalet Hotel Ratings</strong></span><br /><br />To help you with your chalet, Xtra Chalets and Chalet Hotel choice, we show our diamond chalet symbol rating as a guide to help you compare between our chalets, Xtra Chalets and Chalet Hotels as follows:</p>
<p><strong>◆ ◆ ◆</strong> A simple but comfortable, offering excellent value for money.<br /><strong>◆ ◆ ◆ ◆</strong> Superior levels of style and comfort in all living areas and generally with en suite bathroom facilities in most rooms<br /><strong>◆ ◆ ◆ ◆ ◆</strong> Our top chalets in terms of style, comfort and facilities.</p>
<p><span>As chalets, Xtra Chalets and Chalet Hotels do not have official ratings, our ratings are based on Inghams senior management inspections, coupled with guest feedback where applicable, and cannot be compared to standard hotel star ratings. For more information see our </span><a href="/legal/terms-conditions" title="Terms and conditions">terms and conditions</a><span> for details</span></p>
